{"tid":511970,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪拍拖之後，就好難維持友情","createTime":"2017-12-28T04:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T07:40:02.000Z","uid":7803,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"48cf0f8d8386b4adda7a70c967407ee90e9c6fd8","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"拍拖之後，感覺上少咗好多朋友咁。<br />\n因為好多時間都係陪女朋友，同朋友出街既時間少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n未拍拖之前，成日都出黎打下邊爐，做下運動。大家講下之前，開開心心又一日。一齊計劃下去CAMP，幾個男仔去旅行。<br />\n<br />\n但依家拍拖之後，同女朋友雖然好開心，但好似少咗友情依一部分。好似得我先有依個問題，係IG FACEBOOK，見到其他人都可以好似愛情友情 好平衡咁。<br />\n<br />\n係唔係我既問題? 事實上，圈子入面得我有女朋友，如果我帶埋女朋友出黎玩，好似又唔係幾好。"},{"pid":"53ae6da6df4113db546deae1fdc65f6b35391f8d","tid":511970,"uid":84481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"無可避免"},{"pid":"2a713a89a3fd78291ee7b361254a9b35ef109f57","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f699268d929d29f48438ae428c4eea7cf23fa888","tid":511970,"uid":65877,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"唔好比藉口自己 有心就會keep到"},{"pid":"a6056693e9a1c7a19cca3ca140ed236ef8e7e1c4","tid":511970,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"首先就係要將女朋友帶入你既朋友圈<br />\n<br />\n例如聖誕節咁 未必剩係同女友過<br />\n<br />\n可以約一大班人出去PARTY, BBQ 等等<br />\n<br />\n當然 前提係你既朋友圈都OK 或者大家都攜眷出席"},{"pid":"8b4f9ba1529a784c3a8b4fcad26c8b1cb6e2705c","tid":511970,"uid":20914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"好明顯係你問題啦"},{"pid":"af0cf73ee2e4067aac1066bc4771886aff65759a","tid":511970,"uid":148724,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a6056693e9a1c7a19cca3ca140ed236ef8e7e1c4","tid":511970,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"首先就係要將女朋友帶入你既朋友圈<br />\n<br />\n例如聖誕節咁 未必剩係同女友過<br />\n<br />\n可以約一大班人出去PARTY, BBQ 等等<br />\n<br />\n當然 前提係你既朋友圈都OK 或者大家都攜眷出席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"將女友帶入個圈子, 除左等大家可以一齊玩之外<br />\n<br />\n最重要係比女友都暸解你既朋友<br />\n一來比佢信心 好似認定佢所以先會帶返屋企見家長咁既感覺<br />\n二來佢熟下你既朋友, 下次兄弟約食飯甚至去旅行 佢都大概知咩事放心好多"},{"pid":"ee740a7fbc5dc1570e10e957dee14b50eac25b14","tid":511970,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友有共同朋友 無呢個問題<br />\n但其他朋友的確見少左"},{"pid":"57e7b0f461240c1f5d23ec24c8475ced774cfab9","tid":511970,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"少見一定正常架"},{"pid":"5045843c116ba94a15b71ad7bf56ce79cfa53bfc","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b4f9ba1529a784c3a8b4fcad26c8b1cb6e2705c","tid":511970,"uid":20914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"好明顯係你問題啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"咩問題呢?"},{"pid":"5f37d82e59ee7d15c2fd181babddee58e3f99bed","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee740a7fbc5dc1570e10e957dee14b50eac25b14","tid":511970,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友有共同朋友 無呢個問題<br />\n但其他朋友的確見少左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"我地都有共同朋友，共同朋友無依個情況<br />\n反而之前既同學就有依個問題"},{"pid":"8bf23b7c5fbe67a0263190d6538269c0c929ed81","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e7b0f461240c1f5d23ec24c8475ced774cfab9","tid":511970,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"少見一定正常架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"所以唔知點樣可以解決到依個問題"},{"pid":"489f62da9e63f2d0c326d07375d46674846392f2","tid":511970,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bf23b7c5fbe67a0263190d6538269c0c929ed81","tid":511970,"uid":7803,"like":0,"disli